OL,3,CStudy suggests majority of NI adults
OL,4,Cexperienced trauma during childhood
OL,6,FA new study led by Queen's University
OL,7,Fhas highlighted the ongoing influence
OL,8,Fof paramilitaries on life in Northern
OL,9,FIreland nearly 27 years after the Good
OL,10,FFriday Agreement.
OL,12,FThe majority of adults who took part
OL,13,Fin the groundbreaking study reported
OL,14,Fat least one traumatic event in their
OL,15,Fchildhood.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, 30% reported suffering
OL,18,Ftrauma specific to the Troubles, with
OL,19,Fa high number saying they had
OL,20,Fwitnessed violence.
