OL,3,CStudy suggests majority of NI adults
OL,4,Cexperienced trauma during childhood
OL,6,FJustice Minister Naomi Long said the
OL,7,Fresults of the study into Adverse
OL,8,FChildhood Experiences among the
OL,9,Fregion's adult population represent a
OL,10,Fmajor public health challenge.
OL,12,FMs Long said: "For the first time, the
OL,13,Ftrue extent of childhood trauma and
OL,14,Fits impact on all people in Northern
OL,15,FIreland has been documented and
OL,16,Fmeasured for all to see."
