OL,3,CStudy suggests majority of NI adults
OL,4,Cexperienced trauma during childhood
OL,6,F"The findings from this research are
OL,7,Fboth striking and sobering. We now
OL,8,Fhave crucial evidence of how childhood
OL,9,Ftrauma shapes life outcomes in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,12,F"The findings show clear correlations
OL,13,Fbetween higher exposure to trauma in
OL,14,Fchildhood and many negative outcomes,
OL,15,Fincluding poorer educational
OL,16,Fachievement, chronic health conditions
OL,17,Flike rheumatoid arthritis and chronic
OL,18,Fpain, increased exposure to domestic
OL,19,Fviolence, addiction, poor mental
OL,20,Fhealth and health-harming behaviours.
