OL,3,CStudy suggests majority of NI adults
OL,4,Cexperienced trauma during childhood
OL,6,F"These are significant findings which
OL,7,Fwill impact and inform policy and
OL,8,Fdelivery across the Executive."
OL,10,FDr Colm Walsh, an academic at Queen's
OL,11,FUniversity Belfast who led the study,
OL,12,Fsaid: "What we see here is the long
OL,13,Farm of early adversities, the impact
OL,14,Fof which extends beyond childhood,
OL,15,Faffecting a number of key outcomes,
OL,16,Franging from educational attainment,
OL,17,Fphysical and mental health, substance
OL,18,Fuse, and offending.
