OL,3,CStudy suggests majority of NI adults
OL,4,Cexperienced trauma during childhood
OL,6,F"Compared with those who report no
OL,7,FACEs, those who reported four or more
OL,8,Fwere almost nine times more likely to
OL,9,Fbe excluded from school as a child,
OL,10,Feight times more likely to have been
OL,11,Farrested, and three times more likely
OL,12,Fto have used illicit drugs in the
OL,13,Fprevious year as an adult."
OL,15,FThe research was initiated following
OL,16,Fobservations of high trauma levels
OL,17,Famong participants in the Executive
OL,18,FProgramme on Paramilitarism and
OL,19,FOrganised Crime.
