OL,6,FAdverse Childhood Experiences are
OL,7,Fdefined as traumatic or stressful
OL,8,Fexperiences that occur in childhood,
OL,9,Fincluding physical, sexual, emotional
OL,10,Fabuse, neglect, exposure to domestic
OL,11,Fabuse, parental separation, growing up
OL,12,Fin a household where there are adults
OL,13,Fwith mental health or drug or alcohol
OL,14,Fproblems or who have spent time in
OL,15,Fprison.
OL,17,FResearchers surveyed 1,200
OL,18,Fparticipants from Northern Ireland,
OL,19,Femploying internationally recognised
OL,20,Fmethodology.
